data.description: PRICED TO SELL !! Situated in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Ocean Shores,this magnificent, solidly built CBS house promises an unrivaled experience with its exclusive view of the captivating harbor and marina across the street where your boat can be kept.   It sits on a clean 6900 sf lot. The property is one of the few in the area with the unique feature of having access from both the front and the back yards.  This home is completely fenced-in for extra privacy.  Granite countertop extends up the wall for a beautiful backsplash in the main kitchen upstairs. The kitchen also has a built-in pot filler for convenience while cooking.  All three full bathrooms boast oversized showers with multiple showerheads in each.   Four Ring cameras/floodlights and alarms are included in the purchase.  The home's huge yard is ready for parking your boat and RV or building your private oasis with plenty of space for a pool and lots of room left over. Key Largo Park is just a short walk away as is The Pilot House and other restaurants with a diverse selection of food.The home offers three spacious bedrooms and two full baths upstairs and a legally permitted full bathroom located downstairs, providing convenience and privacy for your guests. The home's charm extends outdoors with a wrap-around balcony so you can enjoy your morning coffee watching the sunrise over the harbor. The kitchen also offers a breathtaking view of the harbor, making every cooking and dining experience a memorable one.  Entry stairs are located under roof for those rainy days.  Downstairs offers plenty of storage space with an air-conditioned, large enclosed area and screened-in porch.   Furnishings can be included in separate transaction.  The owners are eagerly awaiting your offers. Don't miss this golden opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Key Largo. Your dream home is just an offer away! Owner/Agent
